gender	category	Male / Female / Other
dob	date	Date of birth
city	string	City or village (e.g., Bidar, Humnabad, Basavakalyan)
state	string	Always â€œKarnatakaâ€
dept_id	int	Foreign key â†’ departments.dept_id
admission_year	int	Year of admission
category	category	SC / ST / OBC / General
hostel_resident	bool	Whether staying in college hostel
phone	string	Contact number
email	string	Email address

Example Rows:

